              <p>Hi Team,</p>
<p>I am using self-hosted Redash with the docker Images,</p>
<p>Now when I try  to send the invitation the Mail goes to Maildev which is one of the docker images, But I have my own outgoing email services, I have to configure that in self-hosted redash configuration,</p>
<p><strong>How I can configure the outgoing services in Self-Hosted server?</strong></p>
<p>Thanks in Advance.</p>
