            <div class='post' itemprop='text'>
              <p>Hey !<br>
This is my mail configuration under Redash V10.0.1 (self-hosted / docker installation).</p>
<pre><code class="lang-auto">#docker.compose.yml
REDASH_MAIL_SERVER: "mail.gnous.fr" #or smtp.gmail.com
REDASH_MAIL_USE_SSL: "true"
REDASH_MAIL_PORT: "465"
REDASH_MAIL_USERNAME: "example@domain.com"
REDASH_MAIL_PASSWORD: "..."
REDASH_MAIL_DEFAULT_SENDER: "example@domain.com"
REDASH_ENFORCE_CSRF: "true"
SERVER_NAME: ""
REDASH_HOST: "https://domain.com" #or ip_adress:port xxx.xxx.xx.xx:5000
</code></pre>
<p>See you <img src="https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/twitter/slight_smile.png?v=12" title=":slight_smile:" class="emoji" alt=":slight_smile:" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20"></p>
            </div>

